      "value": "<p><em>\"Why do I always get stuck with the icky jobs?\"</em></p><h5 id=\"-strong-benefit-strong-br-\"><strong>Benefit:</strong></h5><p>There are jobs that no one wants, but you figure if anyone should do them it should be you. Once per turn when you would damage a bloodied creature you may add 1d4 to your damage total.</p><h5 id=\"-strong-negative-strong-\"><strong>Negative:</strong></h5><p>The work you do does not make you popular. Other people in your organization or team do not fully trust you and thus are less willing to assist you or share private information with you.</p>",
